draw.palette

Class Create

  • java.lang.Object
    • draw.palette.PaletteEntry
      • draw.palette.Create

  • public class Create
extends PaletteEntry
    User requests to create a new selected element (i.e., Rectangle or Oval). There will me multiple create PaletteEntry objects, differentiated only by their prototype. There is going to be a single CreateHandler that reacts and chooses the element to create based on this prototype. Class supports using the Prototype design pattern to create new elements based on the prototype.
